---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About TechFrontier"
	description="Methodology and Vision"
	pubDate={new Date('2026-02-28')}
>
	<p>
		<strong>TechFrontier</strong> is an automated intelligence briefing designed to identify high-signal technical breakthroughs before they reach mainstream commercial adoption.
	</p>
	<p>
		By programmatically scanning top-tier developer hubs and leveraging Large Language Models (LLMs) for semantic synthesis, we separate foundational architectural shifts from marketing noise. Our focus is squarely on engineering execution, open-source validation, and early-stage capital efficiency.
	</p>
	<h3>Methodology</h3>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Automated Ingestion</strong>: Continuous polling of global tech signals.</li>
		<li><strong>Semantic Filtering</strong>: Leveraging AI to discard noise and extract core value.</li>
		<li><strong>Zero-Noise Delivery</strong>: A minimalist reading experience without distractions.</li>
	</ul>
	<p>
		All content is automatically aggregated and synthesized. We believe in "content as UI".
	</p>
</Layout>
